.DT
lose
Discworld player help
lose

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
lose - Lose person or monster that is following you.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
lose <player/monster>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Causes a player/monster that is following you using the 'follow' command
or similar means to stop following you.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
follow.
.EP
